who we are

oceana is the largest international advocacy organization focused solely on ocean conservation. oceanas mission is to protect and restore our oceans.

get to know oceana


our approach

we lead strategic, directed campaigns that achieve measurable outcomes for the oceans. oceana leverages law, science, grassroots activism, advocacy, and strategic communications to win policy change around the world.

see current campaigns


our impact

we have won more than 300 victories and protected nearly 4 million square miles of ocean.
